    <NOTES>BJCP 11C Strong Bitter target, Fuller's ESB clone direction, full-volume no-sparge on G40. Simple grist calibrated toward the 2018 Fuller's parti-gyle brew sheet: pale + crystal + trace chocolate. Current hop lots: Target 9.6%, Northdown 7.3%, Challenger 7.75% assumed midpoint from 6.5-9.0% bag range, EKG 6.1%. Fermentation schedule: Day 0-2 hold 65.0 F (18.3 C), Day 3 raise to 67.0 F (19.4 C) with one deliberate rouse while active, Day 4-9 hold 68.0 F (20.0 C) through terminal gravity and forced VDK pass, then crash 48-72 hr at 42.0 F (5.6 C). Closed transfer only. Carbonate to 1.9-2.1 vols CO2.</NOTES>
